text: Virginie Jouault (born 24 November 1974 in Calais) is a French volleyball player, and physical education teacher. She played at the 1995 Summer Universiade and Mediterranean Games. She played for Stella Calais, RC France- Villebon, AS La Rochette, USSP Albi, DYS VB. She won the 1993/1994 French Cup with Stella Calais. == References == Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Hauts-de-France Category:Volleyball players Category:People from Pas-de-Calais
